# Currency Converter â€“ Java Project

A console-based Java application that converts currencies using **real-time exchange rates from a REST API**. This project was created as part of the **Pinnacle Labs 2025 Java Development Internship Program**.

##Overview
This Currency Converter allows users to:
- Enter source and target currency codes
- Input an amount to convert
- Get real-time converted results using a live API (ExchangeRate API)

## Technologies Used
- Java (JDK 17)
- IntelliJ IDEA
- REST API (https://api.exchangerate.host)
- Scanner class for user input
- Exception handling and basic input validation

## How to Run
1. Clone this repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git
   cd your-repo-name

## Sample Output
